Clash was blasting the side of his mountain open, slowly tunneling in and
creating many passage ways and complex caverns. It could cause someone to
get lost. He liked it that way. Clash flew up on the outside of the cave and
ripped his ship from the mountain, brining it inside on of the many rooms he
had built by carefully using different lasers and fire. He then sat back and
planned about what he would do next in this war...
